      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To direct the Congressional Budget Office to submit daily reports during the period in which a Government shutdown is in effect on the effects of the shutdown on the economy and the costs of the shutdown to taxpayers, and for other purposes.</title>
